used to get wazuh with no internet connection, but a ssh oconnection to a machine that does

on device with internet download the agent file
ex:
wget https://packages.wazuh.com/4.x/windows/wazuh-agent-4.3.11-1.msi

on device without internet copy file via scp
ex:
scp user@ubuntu-ip:/home/user/wazuh-agent-4.3.11-1.msi C:\Users\YourName\Downloads\

then on no internet device install the agent
ex:
msiexec.exe /i C:\Path\To\wazuh-agent-4.3.11-1.msi /q WAZUH_MANAGER="172.16.200.10" WAZUH_REGISTRATION_SERVER="172.16.200.10" WAZUH_AGENT_GROUP="windows"
NET START WazuhSvc
